title: Ray Dalio ON: How To Discover Your Key Strengths & Make Better Decisions About Your Career
description: On this episode of On Purpose with Jay Shetty, Jay speaks with businessman extraordinaire Ray Dalio about how understanding your unique strengths is vital to succeeding in your career. Take Ray's incredible quiz for yourself to see just what natural strengths you possess and how they can lead to your very own business success: https://assessments.principles.com/
